data.description: Country Oasis!! Make sure to come out and see this 4 Bedroom 3 1/2 bath Beautiful Log Home! Inside you will love the "Home" feel you get standing in the Kitchen. Or The Feeling of amazement seeing the Architectural Beauty in the living room. Home has been updated throughout, from new windows and flooring to the interior being repainted, much more. Outside enjoy the Great Outdoors feeling when hanging out on that 50 Foot Deck watching the Kids Zip on the Zipline and run around the almost 4 acres of Country.
